pages.text: Ars Nouveau 1.9.4 $(li)Conjure Water now extinguishes entities $(li)Portals may now be made from any arcane brick$(li)Carbuncles can now jump! $(li)Carbuncle charms, turrets, and splitters are now cheaper$(li)Adds two new carbuncle colors!$(li)Adds tooltips to carbuncles$(li)Volcanic Accumulators now output to their closest chest.
